ello,

Up to date source code is on github (not sourceforge).
https://github.com/internetarchive/heritrix3

The point where webpage content is fetched is the FetchHTTP processor for
http and https resources. Other fetchers are responsible for other url
schemes.

As far as developer documentation there is the javadoc:
http://builds.archive.org:8080/javadoc/heritrix-3.x-snapshot/
Some other documentation which may be useful is listed here:
https://webarchive.jira.com/wiki/display/Heritrix/Heritrix#Heritrix-Documentation

Noah


